OL,6,FGuernsey Dairy has been operating at a
OL,7,Fdeficit for the past five years, with
OL,8,Fcombined losses since 2020 now topping
OL,9,F#1 million, a Freedom of Information
OL,10,Frequest (FOI) has revealed.
OL,12,FThe largest operating deficit after
OL,13,Fdepreciation was in 2022, where it
OL,14,Freached #463,000.
OL,16,FFrom 2020 to the end of 2024, losses
OL,17,Ftotalled #1,126,000.
