OL,6,FThe dairy says the annual operating
OL,7,Floss is a situation "the management
OL,8,Fteam is seeking to address in
OL,9,Fconsultation with key stakeholders".
OL,11,FIn February, the dairy decided to
OL,12,Fcease the production of cheese -
OL,13,Fsaying it was necessary to discontinue
OL,14,Fthe product to make room for new milk
OL,15,Fpackaging equipment.
OL,17,FHowever, the FOI also revealed that
OL,18,Fwhen the costs of production were
OL,19,Fconsidered, each kilogram of cheese
OL,20,Fmade a loss of #2.37.
