OL,6,FThe volume of milk processed to meet
OL,7,Fsales has declined by 14% since 2015,
OL,8,Fwith the dairy citing the "growing
OL,9,Fpopularity and consumption of milk
OL,10,Falternatives perceived as healthier"
OL,11,Fas one of the reasons why.
OL,13,FWhilst over 5.6 million litres of
OL,14,Fcow's milk were sold by the dairy in
OL,15,F2020, only 5.4 million litres were
OL,16,Fsold last year.
OL,18,FThere has also been a decline in the
OL,19,Fnumber of all types of dairy products
OL,20,F- including cheese, cream, and butter
OL,21,F- produced year-on-year.
