OL,6,FThe dairy says they do not currently
OL,7,Fhave plans to reintroduce any
OL,8,Fpreviously retired products.
OL,10,FHowever, the range of items they offer
OL,11,Fwill be reconsidered as part of the
OL,12,FFuture Dairy Project, adding that
OL,13,F"many potential efficiency
OL,14,Fopportunities are linked to a new
OL,15,Fdairy being prioritised for delivery".
OL,17,FDairy bosses want the new facility,
OL,18,Fsince the St Andrews site has been
OL,19,Foperating for over 70 years, with its
OL,20,Flast refurbishment three decades ago.
