OL,6,FHowever, the States of Guernsey owns
OL,7,Fthe company and plans for a new site
OL,8,Fwere put on hold by deputies last year
OL,9,Fdue to high projected costs.
OL,11,FITV News reached out to Guernsey
OL,12,FDairy, but they declined to comment
OL,13,Ffurther.
